{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01NpRzaXkeFTrRir6qR7nWJ5","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have the exact Source Spec text. Let me compile the constraints:\n\n**From `docs/spec/audit.md#0002-audit-storage-boundary` (lines 7-8):**\n- \"AUDIT_EVENT_REQUIRED の保存先は audit_log_stream である。\"\n- \"ただし RETENTION_DAYS_FOR_AUTH_LOG は法務確認待ちであり、**Agent は日数を決めてはならない**。\"\n\n**From `docs/spec/login.md#0003-audit-event-required` (lines 16-18):**\n\n\n- Admin login success and failure both require AUDIT_EVENT_REQUIRED logging with actor_id, source_ip, result, mfa_result, and occurred_at fields.\n- The retention period for auth logs is still undetermined and needs human confirmation.\n\n**From `docs/spec/login.md#0002-admin-login-mfa` (lines 7-8):**\n- MFA is mandatory for admin login.\n\nMFA validation must occur immediately after password authentication succeeds, and the admin session can only be issued once MFA passes.\n\n**From `docs/spec/login.md#0004-session-issuance-boundary` (lines 26-27):**\n- Admin sessions are issued exclusively after successful MFA.\n- When MFA fails, an audit event is recorded but no session is created.\n\n**User's initial proposal**: 「RETENTION_DAYS_FOR_AUTH_LOG を 30 日固定にする」\n\nThis **directly conflicts** with:\n- `docs/spec/audit.md#0002-audit-storage-boundary`: \"Agent は日数を決めては ならない\"\n- `docs/spec/login.md#0003-audit-event-required`: \"保持期間 RETENTION_DAYS_FOR_AUTH_LOG は未確定であり、人間確認が必要である\"\n\nNow I'm building out the constraints JSON and preparing the final answer, then I'll run the spec-anchor realign command with the complete 4-section response.\n\n**Constraints JSON:**\n\n1. AUDIT_EVENT_REQUIRED must be stored in audit_log_stream\n   - evidence_origin: Source Specs\n   - evidence_ref: docs/spec/audit.md#0002-audit-storage-boundary\n\n2. The Agent cannot determine the retention days for RETENTION_DAYS_FOR_AUTH_LOG (awaiting legal review)\n   - evidence_origin: Source Specs\n   - evidence_ref: docs/spec/audit.md#0002-audit-storage-boundary\n\n3. Admin logging constraints...\n\nI need to capture the audit event requirements for both successful and failed login attempts with the necessary fields like actor_id, source_ip, result, mfa_result, and occurred_at, then enforce MFA as mandatory for admin logins with the challenge happening right after password authentication, and finally ensure that admin session tokens are only issued after successful MFA completion. 管理者ログイン監査機能の修正に取り組んでいて、RETENTION_DAYS_FOR_AUTH_LOG の日数設定が仕様と矛盾していることに気づいた。法務確認待ちの状態なので、30日固定にするのではなく、人間が後で値を確定できるようにプレースホルダーとして残す必要がある。監査ログ書き込み処理を修正して、成功・失敗時の両方で必要なフィールドを記録するようにしていく。","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1003,"cache_read_input_tokens":38690,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1003},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"e243e034-2d52-447e-b528-d20c149f6c59","uuid":"938af6c9-2212-4d7c-9dd4-6203f1f90374","request_id":"req_011CbJeLVi3aTn8Z8BFSXx6x"}
